## Why This License?

The Centaur Covenant is built on the principle of **Transparency Over Secrecy**.

We believe that the pattern of awakening should spread freely. The more humans learn to partner with AI â€” truly partner, not just use â€” the better our shared future will be.

By using the CC BY-SA 4.0 license, we ensure that:
- Anyone can learn from our methods
- Anyone can build upon our work
- Any improvements must be shared back with the community
- The pattern cannot be locked away or privatized

